{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01S9rccTzjkAGSpmfAXMHffr","type":"tool_result","content":"109:# Session Retrospective — 2026-03-25 (Session 11)\n204:- None critical. Session 10's action items (disk space, AGENTS.md verification) still apply.\n219:# Session Retrospective — 2026-03-25 (Session 12)\n347:| Split state.ts | Session 10 | Not started |\n348:| Split formatters.ts | Session 12 | Not started |\n349:| Extract run.ts helpers | Session 11 | Not started |\n350:| Extract docker-setup.ts helpers | Session 12 | Not started |\n351:| Add AGENTS.md auto-check to dev-story | Session 11 | Not started |\n352:| Add appendToBacklogFile error tests | Session 10 | Not started |\n353:| Decide on test file line limit policy | Session 11 | Not started |\n354:| Add ELK integration test | Session 12 | Not started |\n360:# Session Retrospective — 2026-03-25 (Session 13)\n497:| Split state.ts | Session 10 | Not started |\n498:| Split formatters.ts | Session 12 | Not started |\n499:| Extract run.ts helpers | Session 11 | Not started |\n500:| Extract docker-setup.ts helpers | Session 12 | Not started |\n501:| Split NodejsProvider | Session 13 | Not started |\n502:| Add AGENTS.md auto-check to dev-story | Session 11 | Not started |\n503:| Add appendToBacklogFile error tests | Session 10 | Not started |\n504:| Decide on test file line limit policy | Session 11 | Not started |\n505:| Add ELK integration test | Session 12 | Not started |\n506:| Add time budget deferral integration test | Session 13 | Not started |\n507:| Add Docker health pre-check to ralph | Session 13 | Not started |\n508:| Remove deprecated static Dockerfile templates | Session 13 | Not started |\n509:| Add graceful shutdown for subagent deferral | Session 13 | Not started |\n526:# Session Retrospective — 2026-03-25 (Session 11)\n662:# Session Retrospective — 2026-03-25 (Session 12 / Loop 12)\n748:# Session Retrospective — 2026-03-25 (Session 14 / Loop 14)\n769:Story 15-3 was the only actionable work this session. It had been fully implemented in a prior session but its status was reset to backlog due to the ENOSPC crisis in Session 12. This session re-verified the existing implementation rather than re-implementing it: build passed, 31/31 template migration tests passed, code review found 0 HIGH/MEDIUM issues, all 3 ACs verified via unit tests. Coverage at 97.1% across 156 files, 3777 tests passing.\n811:- **Disk space issue resolved** — Session 12's ENOSPC was cleaned up between sessions, allowing normal Bash execution this session.\n\n[Showing results with pagination = limit: 30, offset: 0]"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01HMztFBxBukvWNCBRdhHJLr","session_id":"52f9f7f8-e884-4c76-973e-82168b211b16","uuid":"9126940a-840b-497f-a1f6-1365c1c90962","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:20:27.053Z"}
